{"tid":2152310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府借武漢肺炎引入無牌醫護","createTime":"2020-08-12T02:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T15:02:48.000Z","uid":240256,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef72075ac1b8f6348d306268007790c820eb0c3","tid":2152310,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">為咗鋪路俾中國醫護落嚟香港執業，政府已經默默做緊嘢。</span><br />\n<br />\n因為要搞全民檢疫，港共乘機刊憲 臨時豁免國家認可的實驗室檢測人員在港的註冊要求，<span class=\"red\">暫</span>為期兩個月。「中共核酸檢測支援隊」嗰60條友走嚟香港執業，豁免強制檢疫之餘，仲要唔洗註冊、考牌。<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/08/20200807/20200807_205215_439.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020%2F08%2F20200807%2F20200807_205215_439.html&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=6975277d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/08/20200807/20200807_205215_439.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次政府又善用法律武器，因為《輔助醫療條例》寫明 食物及衛生局局長有權豁免任何指明界別的人，即係陳肇始話乜就乜，我真係唔知個立法理據/原意係咩。 <a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap359!zh-Hant-HK@2014-03-03T00:00:00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap359%21zh-Hant-HK%402014-03-03T00%3A00%3A00&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=e0b8e0c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap359!zh-Hant-HK@2014-03-03T00:00:00</a><br />\n<br />\n政府知道會有反對聲音，就搵咗個「業界代表」幫手維穩，話咩「暫時豁免好過容許註冊」，即係搵一舊屎同另一舊屎比較邊舊好食。佢又話咩豁免期只有兩個月，所以唔洗驚。醒下啦，係<span class=\"red\">暫時</span>只有兩個月呀。如果真心為本地業界著想嘅，應該堅持遵守註冊程序，唔合資格就冇得喺本地合法執業。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4YnY4z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4YnY4z.png&h=843ae31c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講，如果真係想請教「中國專家」，叫佢哋做下顧問俾下意見就足夠，唔需要容許佢哋喺到執業。之後出咗咩事，因為佢哋唔洗註冊，市民根本無法追究，個「業界代表」都講到明，佢哋犯錯，公司負責嫁咋，佢哋可以拍下籮柚走人。<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/32704/內地核酸檢測支援隊-醫務化驗師-豁免註冊-32704/豁免註冊 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F32704%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%B8%E9%85%B8%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E9%9A%8A-%E9%86%AB%E5%8B%99%E5%8C%96%E9%A9%97%E5%B8%AB-%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E8%A8%BB%E5%86%8A-32704%2F%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E8%A8%BB%E5%86%8A%20&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=35f964f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/32704/內地核酸檢測支援隊-醫務化驗師-豁免註冊-32704/豁免註冊 </a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">今次豁免化驗師，下次就係醫生護士，唔好覺得唔關自己事。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有，政府妥託間九唔搭八嘅中龍檢驗認證有限公司，佢啲認可主要係關於玩具同埋兒童產品，驗玩具點同驗肺炎呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cpsc.gov/cgi-bin/LabSearch/ViewDetail.aspx?ReqId=WmWxqozJbnJPx%2ftrXjECFg%3d%3d&amp;LabId=JlAjy2xzgz74YCxg64ZrMQ%3d%3d \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cpsc.gov%2Fcgi-bin%2FLabSearch%2FViewDetail.aspx%3FReqId%3DWmWxqozJbnJPx%252ftrXjECFg%253d%253d%26LabId%3DJlAjy2xzgz74YCxg64ZrMQ%253d%253d%20&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=43023fe8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cpsc.gov/cgi-bin/LabSearch/ViewDetail.aspx?ReqId=WmWxqozJbnJPx%2ftrXjECFg%3d%3d&amp;LabId=JlAjy2xzgz74YCxg64ZrMQ%3d%3d </a>"},{"pid":"84512fb17c78bc4c26ec2ee6ed709a04855161df","tid":2152310,"uid":48132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:17:01.000Z","msg":"好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae837951bd07cd5b619d32b754085d8bc9a9354c","tid":2152310,"uid":240256,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:22:32.000Z","msg":"個所謂「業界代表」露晒底，紅底。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tncW3WE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtncW3WE.png&h=d536f924&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bFQ8ok.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bFQ8ok.png&h=fe4bb7c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkaml.org/index.php/chairman-s-message\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkaml.org%2Findex.php%2Fchairman-s-message&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=5d47cd98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkaml.org/index.php/chairman-s-message</a>"},{"pid":"f1b2a4b6b90c308ff467ab710ffb6043198645c7","tid":2152310,"uid":240256,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:25:38.000Z","msg":"陳肇始憑咩話事？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPBtaDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPBtaDa.jpg&h=9c4e2a89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05b9bc5a9f39367db47cbd5662c2589585137b10","tid":2152310,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:27:21.000Z","msg":"Med lab 啲人死剩佢一個？成日搵佢做訪問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542247-20200806.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542247-20200806.html&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=3be747ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542247-20200806.html&h=c7a9cddd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542247-20200806.html</a>"},{"pid":"6f5b3caacf65d92911dde8d42ae4806bdc9d1a9c","tid":2152310,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:27:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9ee78bd711f3f9089e16ea843e6550fe562791d","tid":2152310,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:28:26.000Z","msg":"呢個要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚賤"},{"pid":"d7b2b07ebd36d38a47dc95a83b4986c72dea9fb4","tid":2152310,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:30:15